===Rejected memberships===
[[Scott Summers (Earth-616)|Cyclops]] has proposed a few heroes to join, in vain:
* The [[Avengers (Earth-616)|Avenger]] [[Carol Danvers (Earth-616)|Carol Danvers]] (as Captain Marvel) was offered membership by [[Scott Summers (Earth-616)|Cyclops]], in regard to her common past with the [[X-Men (Earth-616)|X-Men]], and for the memory of [[Charles Xavier (Earth-616)|Charles Xavier]], but a brawl occurred soon after between the two teams.{{r|Uncanny X-Men Vol 3 3}}
* [[Calvin Rankin (Earth-616)|Mimic (Calvin Rankin)]] and [[Michael Pointer (Earth-616)|Omega (Michael Pointer)]] were proposed, but rejected the offer, as they wanted to help common people and not battle among heroes.{{r|X-Men: Legacy #300}}
